com.salesforce.androidsdk.analytics.model

Class InstrumentationEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.salesforce.androidsdk.analytics.model.InstrumentationEvent

  • public class InstrumentationEvent
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a typical instrumentation event. Transforms can be used to convert this event into a specific library's event format.

    bhariharan
